column4: We would like to invite every body to take part in this party,  per person £50, student discount 10%. Our main guets in this event are Mr. Alpha, Mrs. Bravo, Miss Charlie and Mr. Delta. It will start at 19:30 in the evening and closes around 1am in the morning. Please do not forget to bring this mobile phone to show us if you want to consider for discount. Thank you -- Management Team
